
  <sn><md>### Style

Style is a gentle and professionalism in dress, gesture, haircut, and overall appearance.

Appearance is the first thing that people notice. It creates fear and nervousness on the opposite side and transforms into confidence on the self side.

It does not mean modern or expensiveness, just gentleness and professionalism in personality.
</md></sn>
